import React, {Component} from "react"; import InfiniteCarousel from 'react-leaf-carousel'; import './Carousel.css' class Carousel extends Component { render(){ return (
breakpoints={[ { breakpoint: 500, settings: { slidesToShow: 2, slidesToScroll: 2, }, }, { breakpoint: 768, settings: { slidesToShow: 3, slidesToScroll: 3, }, }, ]} dots={true} showSides={true} sidesOpacity={.5} sideSize={.1} slidesToScroll={4} slidesToShow={4} scrollOnDevice={true} >
); } } export default Carousel;
